{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}West Bridgford{\*\xmlclose} I went out to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}South Africa{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. And worked my way round - South 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Africa{\*\xmlclose} for four years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 How old were you when you went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
