\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 Who would spank you, either of your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid404251 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 Pop - pop would do the spanking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 Did your mother ever spank you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid404251 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 No. Never spanked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 Can you remember any occasion when you had a good ticking-off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid404251 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 
No, I was trying to think, quite honestly I can't. I - I know - the biggest - sort of - upset was w
hen - we had to go to church and Sunday school of course three times on Sunday. Well - somebody wrote an anonymous letter to pop and said that I was - mixed up with one of the choirboys. The last thing on earth that would have appealed to me, I've never -
 
I've never had that sort of feeling. And so of course - after a - I found out afterwards after a terrific discussion between me and mother as to whether it was anything or not, they sent for my - girl pal, and she - told them that it was all bunkim, or wh
a
tever word she used in those days. Still alive that girl, Nell. Said, no, there was - it was all a pack of lies. And - so mother and father tackled me about it, and they told me they'd had this letter. It wasn't anonymous now I come to think of it, the gi
rl's name was at the end and she was another girl that was at Mandealla, and why she did it to this day I don't know, but - that upset me terribly.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 But that was all discussed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid404251 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 It was all discussed and aired. But I couldn't understand why anybody
 should say such a thing. Because - I wasn't interested in boys in that way. And - yes, and roughly speaking I haven't been. But that was the only big emotional do I can really remember, it was an emotional do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 Were the boys punished in the same way o
r were they treated differently when they were older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid404251 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 
Well of course - with the old ideas of the difference between the sexes I shouldn't be - in at anything that happened to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 You wouldn't know if they were spanked?
