as I think with our birthdays - anything we particularly wanted during the - year, we - everybody knew about it and we'd get it on our next birthday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4222835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7875416\charrsid11885113 
